# cPanel access (local only — never commit tokens)

Store Spaceship/cPanel shared-access JWTs in your password manager or a local file
outside this repo. Do not commit tokens to git.

If you need Cursor MCP access to cPanel, set env vars locally (not in git):

```
CPANEL_ACCESS_TOKEN=...
CPANEL_ACCESS_URL=https://www.spaceship.com/hosting/tools/cpanel-access/
```
